'The Independent' reports that recording artist Vory says Kanye West will be taking a hiatus from music while: , "battling with his own s---." Vory appeared on three tracks on Ye's 2021 album, 'Donda'. "The person who made me realize my twisted thoughts weren't so twisted was Ye, because we think alike." Vory, via Complex. According to Vory, the two artists have only been able to speak through Ye's personal assistant:, “because [Ye] hasn't been wanting to talk to anybody.”